Ore dake Level Up na Ken

They say whatever doesnt kill you makes you stronger, but thats not the case for the worlds weakest hunter Sung Jinwoo. After being brutally slaughtered by monsters in a high-ranking dungeon, Jinwoo came back with the System, a program only he could see, thats leveling him up in every way. Now, hes inspired to discover the secrets behind his powers and the dungeon that spawned them.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
